const e=[{id:1,title:"Annual Gala Dinner & Awards 2025",slug:"annual-gala-dinner-awards-2025",content:'<div class="event-details"><h2>Join Us for an Evening of Celebration and Recognition</h2><p>The African Christian Business Fellowship (ACBF) Republic of South Africa is thrilled to invite you to our <strong>Annual Gala Dinner & Awards</strong> event. This prestigious evening promises to be a memorable celebration of excellence, fellowship, and the building of lasting legacies in the Christian business community.</p><h3>Event Details</h3><ul><li><strong>Date:</strong> Friday, 28 November 2025</li><li><strong>Time:</strong> 18:00 to 22:00</li><li><strong>Venue:</strong> Emperors Palace, Kempton Park</li></ul><h3>Ticket Information</h3><ul><li><strong>Standard Tickets:</strong> R1,000 per person</li><li><strong>VIP Tickets:</strong> R3,000 per person</li></ul><h3>Theme: Building a Legacy that Lasts. Fruit that Remains</h3><p>This year\'s theme is inspired by the biblical principles of building lasting legacies and producing fruit that remains. We will explore how Christian business leaders can create meaningful impact that extends beyond their immediate success.</p><p><em>"You did not choose me, but I chose you and appointed you so that you might go and bear fruit—fruit that will last—and so that whatever you ask in my name the Father will give you." - John 15:16</em></p><p><em>"Praise the Lord. Blessed are those who fear the Lord, who find great delight in his commands. Their children will be mighty in the land; the generation of the upright will be blessed. Wealth and riches are in their houses, and their righteousness endures forever." - Psalm 112:1-3</em></p><h3>What to Expect</h3><ul><li>Elegant dinner and networking opportunities</li><li>Recognition of outstanding achievements in Christian business</li><li>Inspiring keynote addresses</li><li>Awards ceremony honoring excellence in various categories</li><li>Fellowship with like-minded Christian business leaders</li><li>Entertainment and celebration</li></ul><h3>RSVP Information</h3><p><strong>RSVP Deadline: 15 November 2025</strong></p><p>To secure your place at this prestigious event, please RSVP by the deadline. Spaces are limited, and early booking is recommended.</p><h3>Contact Information</h3><ul><li><strong>ACBF RSA:</strong> +27 76 775 0044</li><li><strong>G Chinomona:</strong> +27 73 416 3323</li><li><strong>Email:</strong> Info@acbf.org.za</li><li><strong>Website:</strong> www.acbf.org.za</li></ul><h3>Dress Code</h3><p>Formal/Black Tie attire is requested for this elegant evening.</p><p>We look forward to celebrating with you and building lasting legacies together in the Christian business community.</p></div>',excerpt:"Join us for the Annual Gala Dinner & Awards on 28 November 2025 at Emperors Palace, Kempton Park. An evening of celebration, recognition, and fellowship. Theme: Building a Legacy that Lasts. Fruit that Remains.",featuredImage:null,author:"ACBF RSA",date:"2025-11-28",categories:["Events","Announcements"],tags:["Gala Dinner","Awards","Networking","Fellowship","2025"]}];export{e as p};
